# xclarity_location_to_site — map XClarity location.location values to NetBox site names
# Format: regex_pattern,replacement
# Lines starting with # are ignored.
# The first matching pattern wins; the original value is returned unchanged if nothing matches.
#
# Examples:
#   ^DataCenter1$,DC1
#   ^DataCenter2$,DC2
#   (?i)^main.*,Main Campus
